Solution ahead!

:beginner: Basic Code Solution:
------
~~~
function findLongestWord(str) {
  str = str.split(" ").map(function(val){
    return val.length;
  });
  
  return Math.max.apply(null, str);
}

findLongestWord("The quick brown fox jumped over the lazy dog");
~~~

:rocket: [Run Code](https://repl.it/CLjU/5)

### Code Explanation:

First split the string into an array, Create a new array which contains the length of each array,and then return the max length from the array.

